\par }\pard \li863\sa100\sl240\slmult0 {\f4\cf1 Wordz, Resultz and Fireworkz are part of the Z family of applications from Colton Software. 
\par You can use Wordz alone as a word processor to write letters, reports, books, invitations, shopping lists, schedules and other documents. 
\par You can use Resultz alone as a spreadsheet to perform calculations, analyse figures, and produce colourful charts. 
\par Fireworkz combines these two members of the family enabling you to do even more\emdash incorporate live results in your reports, or automatic mail-merge to your friends or customers, for example. 
\par Once you have learned to use one of these programs you will find it easy to use the other members of the family, because they share much of the same interface and have been designed to work well together. This is true even if you move from RISC-
OS to Windows or vice versa; the programs have been designed to be as similar as possible on each platform.\page }{\f4\fs36\cf1 About this Getting Started Guide
\par }{\f4\cf1 This Getting Started Guide includes all the information you need to install and start using Colton Fireworkz. You can find more information about the program and its features in the on-line help and in the User Guide and Spreadsheet Guide.

\par This Getting Started Guide includes:
\par }\pard \fi-216\li1080\sa100\sl240\slmult0\tx1080 {\f4\cf1 A brief installation guide
